message:
Want to share with you guys an event for engineers and aspiring leaders who want to learn more about important engineering tools that lead engineers from companies like Soda Labs, Scalable Press, Pic Collage, and Autopass are thankful for.

Event page: https://www.facebook.com/events/415581102700515/

Date & time: November 26, 2019 | 6PM - 9PM

Location: Appworks (By Taipei City Hall MRT Station)

-

#免費工程師講座 #工程師meetup

感恩節將至，Soda Labs 與 Scalable Labs 聯合主辦的免費工程師講座來囉！

本次的Soda Series活動邀請了來自Scalable Press、Pic Collage、Autopass以及Soda Labs的首席工程師來跟各位分享他們所感謝的Engineering Tools，提供餐點及飲品，活動採報名制但完全免費，歡迎大家來聽講！

活動時間：2019年11月26日 (二) 18:00-21:00

活動地點：AppWorks （靠近市政府捷運站）
